OL,5, The boss of a housing association which
OL,6, rented out a mouldy flat to Awaab      
OL,7, Ishak's family has been sacked.        
OL,9,FThe board said it has "taken the       
OL,10,Fdecision to remove Gareth Swarbrick    
OL,11,Ffrom his post as chief executive of RBH
OL,12,Fwith immediate effect".                
OL,14,FTwo-year-old Awaab died in 2020 after  
OL,15,Fexposure to mould in his home, a       
OL,16,Fcoroner concluded this week.           
OL,18,FHis father repeatedly raised the issue 
OL,19,Fwith Rochdale Boroughwide Housing (RBH)
OL,20,Fbut no action was taken.               
